  'setting_vf_related_allow_top200' => '<title>Related: Allow Top200 Videos</title><info>Set this to true to include Top200 Videos in the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result.</info>',
  'setting_vf_related_force_same_body_style' => '<title>Related: Force Same Body Style</title><info>Set this to true to only include Videos of vehicles of the same Body Style as the Video currently being played or last played in the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result.</info>',
  'setting_vf_related_force_same_make' => '<title>Related: Force Same Make</title><info>Set this to true to only include Videos of vehicles of the same Make as the Video currently being played or last played in the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result.</info>',
  'setting_vf_related_force_same_model' => '<title>Related: Force Same Model</title><info>Set this to true to only include Videos of vehicles of the same Model as the Video currently being played or last played in the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result.</info>',
  'setting_vf_related_force_same_year' => '<title>Related: Force Same Year</title><info>Set this to true to only include Videos of vehicles of the same Year as the Video currently being played or last played in the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result.</info>',
  'setting_vf_related_max_videos' => '<title>Related: Maximum Videos</title><info>Set this to limit the total number of Videos included.

In order for all selected Makes to be represented, if the total number of Videos exceeds this number because of multiple Makes, the number of Videos per Make will be lowered until the total amount of Videos is less than or equal to this number.</info>',
  'setting_vf_related_max_videos_per_make' => '<title>Related: Maximum Videos Per Make</title><info>Set this to limit the number of Videos included in the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result for each of a dealer&#039;s selected Makes.</info>',
  'setting_vf_related_round_robin' => '<title>Related: Round Robin Sort</title><info>Example: If eight Videos total are to be included in the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result being of three different Makes, AA, BBB, CCC, set this to false to leave the Videos in the order they were returned from the database, the order in which they were added, which may produce seemingly arbitrary results.

Set this to true so that a Video from each make appears on the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result before two Videos of the same Make are added to the playlist of Related Videos as returned with a Video Select Drop Down Search Result, ABC, ABC, BC.</info>',
  'setting_vf_video_select_allowed_years' => '<title>Video Select: Allowed Years</title><info>Specify Year(s) to select only a vehicle from the Year(s) entered here as the Video Select Drop Down Search Result. Leave blank to include all Years.</info>',
